room_title: Escape room "Jail Escape Game" by Escape the Cabin in Gaylord
room_description: While on vacation, you and your fellow outlaws get arrested and locked in jail. While the jail watcher is away, you must utilize teamwork to escape by finding the secrets. There is only a narrow window of opportunity to regain your freedom! Come on vacation, leave on probation or escape in 60 minutes or less.
